Just as we depend upon you, we want you to let us help you. Writing XTMPLs can
be a complicated process and we (the creators) know all the tricks to make it
easier. We want and welcome you to ask us to create and manage your XTMPLs. We
can even wrap the whole product around a Web frontend so that you can give your
users something pretty to look at.

If a vacation is what you need, contact us at <support@goreliance.com>. We will
gladly set up and maintain your text conversion.
